General.Name: CDRL SA
General.Description: CDRL S.A. designs, manufactures, and distributes children's clothing and baby accessories. Its products also include footwear, toys, cosmetics, diapers, food, and furniture. The company sells its products through a chain of stores located in Poland, the Czech Republic, Romania, Belarus, Russia, and other countries. It operates under the Coccodrillo, Lemon Explore, Petit Bijou, Broel, Buslik, and Fikolki Playrooms brands. CDRL S.A. is based in Koscian, Poland.
